# Apprise notification configuration (optional).
# Configure notification targets in the Web UI at /notifications.
# Supported services: Telegram, Discord, Slack, email, Pushover, Gotify, etc.
# See https://github.com/caronc/apprise for URL format examples:
#   tgram://bot_token/chat_id          # Telegram
#   discord://webhook_id/token         # Discord
#   slack://token/a/b/c                # Slack
#   mailto://user:pass@smtp_host       # Email via SMTP
#   gotify://gotify.example.com/token  # Gotify
